@startuml
title C4 Container – US 2.2.13 Qualifications

actor "Logistics\nOperator" as Operator

node "Client Layer" {
  [UI / API Client] as Client
}

node "Web API" {
  [QualificationsController] as Ctl
}

node "Application Layer" {
  [QualificationService] as Svc
}

database "Persistence" as Db
node "Domain" as Dom {
  [Qualification] as Q
  [StaffMember] as Staff
  [PhysicalResource] as Resource
}

Operator --> Client : manage qualifications
Client --> Ctl : POST/PUT/GET/DELETE
Ctl --> Svc : CRUD operations
Svc --> Db : persist/retrieve
Svc ..> Q : create/update
Staff --> Q : requires qualifications
Resource --> Q : requires qualifications

note right of Q
  Qualification:
  - Code (max 15 chars, unique)
  - Name (≥2 words, max 150)
  - Description (optional)
  - Code immutable after creation
  - Referenced by staff/resources
end note

@enduml
